Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:08.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.09,0:18:10.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.26,0:18:18.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是今后请如实汇报
